      "text": [
        " «الْجِيرَانُ أَحَقُّ بِهَا وَ لاَ بَأْسَ أَنْ يُعْطَى قِيمَةُ ذَلِكَ فِضَّةً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2076 - Ishaq ibn Ammar asked Abu Al-Hasan (as) about Zakat al-Fitr.\nImam (as) said: \"Neighbors have the greatest right to it, and there is no harm in giving its equivalent value in silver.\""
        ]
      }
